    <p class="description">A self-serve B2B advertising platform targeting professionals by job title, company, industry, skills, and seniority. Offers precision no other ad network matches for reaching decision-makers — at a <strong>higher cost per click than alternatives</strong>, but with proportionally higher lead quality.</p>
